2011-04-17  Bernhard Walle <bernhard@bwalle.de>

	* Add CMake build open 'BUILD_EXAMPLES' that allows to build the
	  library only.
	* Add SerialFile::readLine() method.
	* Use the SerialFile::readLine() method in the example.
	* SerialFile: Don't return empty strings for each line.
	* SerialFile: Disable translation of \r to \n.

2011-03-06  Bernhard Walle <bernhard@bwalle.de>

	* Don't try to link against libcurses when libreadline has not been
	  found.
	* Change completion interface from ssize_t to int since Win32 has no
	  ssize_t.
	* Add compatibility strcasecmp() for Win32.
	* Only include "unistd.h" if we have it.
	* CMakeLists.txt: Switch to cmakedefine.

